Package dfischer.utils

Apica ZebraTester Library - Used at runtime by the executed load test programs.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ExecutionPlanInterpreterInterface
    An interface that has to be implemented by the caller of the ExecutionPlanInterpreter.
    GenericPluginInterface
    The generic plug-in interface allows to enhance the Proxy Sniffer product with own written utilities.
    GetRealTimeUserInputFieldsInterface
    Supports to get the definition and the value of all real-time user input fields from a running load test job.
    HttpTestURLSetExecutionStepInterface
    Supports to set the internal execution step of an URL call.
    LoadtestPluginInterface
    Allows to define fixed configuration settings for load test plug-ins.
    LogVectorInterface
    Interface to collect ASCII/TEXT log output of a thread and to dump it later in a safe way.
    RunJUnitMethodInterface
    Support to run JUnit test methods in parallel threads.
    SetThreadStepInterface
    An internal interface used for the parallel execution of several URL calls per simulated user.
    SSLSessionCacheStatisticInterface
    Get statistic data about the SSL session cache behavior from a thread (concurrent user).
    SuspendResumeInterface
    Supports to suspend and to resume the execution of running load test job.
    ThreadStepInterface
    Asks a thread (concurrent user) about its current execution step (thread step).
    VarHandlerPluginInterface
    Internal.
    VaryingLoadInterface
    Supports to increment or to decrement the number of simulated users at runtime.
    VaryingTestDurationInterface
    Supports to reduce or to extend the test duration of a running load test job.
    WebSocketPluginInterface
    Allows to define fixed configuration settings for web socket plug-ins.

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ChunkedTransferEncodingProtocolViolationException
    Signals a protocol violation during receiving HTTP chunked transfer encoding data (malformed web server response).
    EncryptionContextNoLongerAvailableException
    Signals that the encryption context of a load test job is no longer available.
    ExecutionPlanRuntimeException
    An exception that signals that an error did occur during the execution of a formal valid execution plan command or function.
    ExecutionPlanSyntaxException
    An exception that signals that a malformed command or function was detected during the parsing of an execution plan.
    InlineScriptExecutionException
    Signals that the execution of an inline script has failed because of a syntax error (invalid script code).
    InlineScriptInterruptedException
    Signals that the execution of an inline script was interrupted.
    InlineScriptTimeoutExceededException
    Signals that the execution timeout of an inline script has exceeded.
    LibGUNZIPException
    Signals that data cannot be unzipped (decompressed).
    LibInflateException
    Signals that data cannot be inflated (decompressed).
    LibSocketConnectTimeoutException
    Signals that a timeout occurred during establishing a TCP/IP socket connection.

Package dfischer.utils Description

Apica ZebraTester Library - Used at runtime by the executed load test programs.
